The canonical definition aligns very well with the provided PDF documentation for UBX-MGA-DBD. The message name, Class ID (0x13), Message ID (0x80), and type (Input/output) all match. The canonical's use of `{"array_of": "U1", "count": "N"}` for the variable `data` field is an appropriate representation for the 'repeated group' described in the PDF, as 'N' is derived from the remaining payload length.
